------------------------------------------------------------------------
Algorithm and test vectors
------------------------------------------------------------------------
This IP implements Ascon-AEAD128 as specified in NIST Special Publication
800-232, "Ascon-Based Lightweight Cryptography Standards for Constrained
Devices." The Ascon algorithm is a public standard; the reference
implementations published by the Ascon team are released into the public
domain (CC0). The RTL and models in this repository are an independent,
clean-room implementation written from the specification.

The known-answer test vectors in tb/vectors/ (LWC_AEAD_KAT_128_128.txt) are
the official Ascon-AEAD128 vectors from the Ascon reference distribution
(https://github.com/ascon/ascon-c), used unmodified for conformance testing.
Test vectors are facts, not creative works; the reference distribution is
CC0 / public domain.
